Package com.teamonehundred.pixelboat

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CollisionObject
    Represents the CollisionObject as an interface.
    Scene
    Represents the interface for all Scenes.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AIBoat
    Represents the AI's boat.
    Boat
    Base class for all boat types.
    BoatRace
    Represents a BoatRace.
    CollisionBounds
    Represents a CollisionBounds object.
    GameObject
    Represents a game object.
    MovableObject
    Represents the movable object as an abstract class that extends from game object.
    Obstacle
    Represents the obstacle as an abstract class that extends from movable object and implements the CollisionObject interface.
    ObstacleBranch
    Represents the simple branch obstacle.
    ObstacleDuck
    Represents the simple duck obstacle.
    ObstacleFloatingBranch
    Represents a floating branch obstacle.
    ObstacleLaneWall
    Represents a lane wall obstacle.
    PixelBoat
    Main class for the PixelBoat game.
    PlayerBoat
    Represents the user player's boat.
    SceneBoatSelection
    Represents the Boat Selection Scene for when the player wants to select which boat to play with before the race starts.
    SceneMainGame
    Represents the Main Game Scene for when the boat race starts.
    SceneOptionsMenu
    Represents the Options Menu Scene for when the player wants to select/edit the options before the race starts.
    SceneResultsScreen
    Scene Class for Results Screen.
    SceneStartScreen
    Represents the Main Game Scene for when the boat race starts.
    SceneTutorial
    Represents the Tutorial Scene for when the player wants to see the controls and learn the purpose of UI elements before the race starts.
